&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you looking for a rewarding job with great pay and benefits?, Do you want to join a company that cares?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Alpha Health Care are Dementia Specialists, providing a person centred, caring and professional service to all our residents in a safe and homely environment. Currently recruiting for a DayStaff Nurse (RMN / RGN / RNLD) to join our specialised team at Lakeview.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The benefits of this staff nurse position include: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- £16.50per hour + excellant benefits including:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Paid breaks &amp; Handover time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- NMC PIN refunded.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Nurse Developmet Workshops&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Subsidised staff meals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Day shifts available - 8am - 8pm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-Company pension scheme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Dedicated revalidation mentor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- In-house training team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Free parking on site&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Easily commutable from Walsall, Wolverhampton, Great Wyrley, Stafford, Cannock, Birmingham and Lichfield&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Uniform provided&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- 5.6 weeks holiday entitlement per year&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Alpha Health Care, we are committed to keeping our staff safe from the risk presented by Coronavirus (COVID-19). We have introduced a number of steps to increase protection for our staff which include increased access to hand washing and hand sanitising facilities, testing protocols, full access to PPE and welfare support for all our staff.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
